{"tid":644164,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【南北韓高峰會】金正恩跨過兩韓軍事分界線 中國網民high：期待兩岸統一","createTime":"2018-04-27T05:00:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-27T08:05:38.000Z","uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":60,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"a3e1727ee2f25c16a433b37c87febb99a6e464ea","tid":644164,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T05:00:55.000Z","msg":"【南北韓高峰會】金正恩跨過兩韓軍事分界線 中國網民high：期待兩岸統一<br />\n<br />\n全球矚目的南北韓高峰會在11點左右落幕。金正恩今年成了朝鮮半島分裂以來第一位踏入<br />\n南韓領土的北韓領導人，針對這個發展，中國一直保持密切注意，中央電視台大幅報導高<br />\n峰會實況。<br />\n<br />\n而中國網民也熱切關切南北韓高峰會動態，有些人聯想到兩岸統一：「讓我們見證歷史。<br />\n我希望台灣有朝一日能－回到中國懷抱。」<br />\n<br />\n也有網民說：「「柏林圍牆倒塌了，北緯38度線模糊了，我希望台灣能跨過海洋，就像走<br />\n失多年的孩子回到母親身邊。」<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/F67Sxp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FF67Sxp&d=ZbLDp%2FSOqoVC0pFaSHQ%2FrzPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=9e41c137\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/F67Sxp</a>"},{"pid":"1d956587c044324fdf6dba88771c1348e935f8e4","tid":644164,"uid":34394,"like":41,"dislike":1,"score":40,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T05:02:09.000Z","msg":"中華民國反攻收復大陸<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92305421c08878035bd0866adba1112f0c4507a2","tid":644164,"uid":143241,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"quote":{"pid":"1d956587c044324fdf6dba88771c1348e935f8e4","tid":644164,"uid":34394,"like":41,"dislike":1,"score":40,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T05:02:09.000Z","msg":"中華民國反攻收復大陸<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T05:03:56.000Z","msg":"大陸是中華民國不可分離的領土"},{"pid":"4984802f129cab94dc14db01b365b339b263fd51","tid":644164,"uid":609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T05:08:29.000Z","msg":"中國或成最大贏家<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ae514c42f127ec2ef995cf9fb44a290f55b2